{Thrash}

    Thrash snarled watching the maximals begin to retreat, his eyes
narrowing as they flew into a cloud that moved odd compared to others.
Screaming at the top of his speakers the drunk missile launcher deep in his
form released another volley of 8 missile, a good half of them flew wildly
away, careening in any random direction other than the departing cloud, but
four seemingly continued on in a random intercept course for the cloud...
